==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sess
<hw>Sess</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Aphetic form of
<ets>assess</ets>. See <er>Assess</er>, <er>Cess</er>.]</ety> <def>To
lay a tax upon; to assess.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

