==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Sess
<hw>Sess</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A tax; an assessment. See
<er>Cess</er>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

